  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0b95\u0bca\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb8\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0b86\u0baa\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b90. \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd: \u0baa\u0bc8\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Al-Qaeda leader Zagiri in Afghanistan Killed in US attack: Biden",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President of the United States Joe Biden said yesterday that the United States killed Al Qaeda leader Ayman al-Zawaghiri last weekend in an attack in Afghanistan.",
        "At 7:18 a.m. Sri Lanka time yesterday in Kabul, the capital of Afghanistan. Swagiri, who did not want to be identified, said he died after an American drone strike. US officials said.",
        "I had high confidence through multiple intelligence channels that the person killed was Savagiri. A senior administration official told reporters that US intelligence confirmed it.",
        "He was killed on the balcony of a safe house that Savagiri shared with other members of his family, and there were no other casualties.",
        "Savagiri has been rumored to have died a few times in recent years and is said to have been in poor health.",
        "Earlier it was said that Zawagiri could be in Pakistan's tribal region or Afghanistan.",
        "In a video released in April this year, Savagiri praised an Indian Muslim woman who crossed a barrier and wore an Islamic face veil.",
        "This year Sawagiri's wife, his daughter and daughter's children were transferred to the said house in Kabul. An official said that the US identified and later identified Savagiri there as well.",
        "Swagiri, who was identified several times on the balcony, was killed there and continued to make videos from there, some of which will be released after his death, the official said.",
        "The spokesman of the Ministry of Interior, Abdul Nafi Thakur, had earlier said that a house was hit by a rocket in Sherpur and there were no casualties as the house was empty.",
        "Meanwhile, a Taliban source, who did not want to be identified, said that a drone flew over Kabul at that time."
      ],
